        </div>
        <div class="home__sub">
          <p>Business strategest, web designer, and developer in New York City working with businesses, entrepeneurs and freelancers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="home__button">
          <a class='btn_block_white' href="#contact">Say Hello!</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="who_i_am">
    <h1 class="who_i_am__title">Hello.</h1>
    <div class="who_i_am__para">
      <p>I’m a business strategy professional turned web designer and developer. I can help you market, design, and launch your freelance website, blog, or startup MVP. </p>
    </div>
    <div class="who_i_am__links">
      <a class="who_i_am__link"href="#contact">CONTACT</a>
      <a class="who_i_am__link"href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/tom-patton">LINKEDIN</a>
      <a class="who_i_am__link" href="https://github.com/tompatton2">GITHUB</a>
      <!-- <a class="who_i_am__link"href="">SKETCH</a> -->
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="what_i_do">
    <h1 class="what_i_do__title">What I do</h1>
    <div class="what_i_do_container">
      <div class="what_i_do__element">
        <%= image_tag "suitcase.svg", class: "what_i_do__icon" %>
        <p class="what_i_do__header">BUSINESS</p>
        <p class="what_i_do__text">My background is in business strategy and management. I've worked with Cisco, Google, and HotelTonight. </p>
      </div>
      <div class="what_i_do__element">
        <%= image_tag "pencil.svg", class: "what_i_do__icon" %>
        <p class="what_i_do__header">DESIGN</p>
        <p class="what_i_do__text">I come from a family of architects and artists. Design is my hobby and passion.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="what_i_do__element">
        <%= image_tag "html.svg", class: "what_i_do__icon" %>
        <p class="what_i_do__header">DEVELOPMENT</p>
        <p class="what_i_do__text">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, te velit iriure has. Vix quem feugiat id. At oblique accusata prodesset vis, eam ad latine vivendum.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="my_work">
    <h1 class="my_work__title">The things I've made</h1>
    <div class="my_work__container">
      <a href="#home">
        <%= image_tag "swapp.svg", class: "carousel_image" %>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="contact">
    <h1 class="contact__title">Let's build together.</h1>
    <div class="contact__container">
      <div class="contact__form">
        <div class="form">
          <%= form_for @inbound do |c| %>
          <div class="form__content">
            <%= c.label :name, "Name" %>
            <%= c.text_field :name %>
            <%= c.label :email, "Email" %>
            <%= c.text_field :email %>
            <%= c.label :message, "Message" %>
            <%= c.text_field :message, :class => 'form__message' %>
          </div>
          <%= c.submit 'Contact Tom', :class => 'btn_transparent_white'%>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="contact__links">
        <a class="contact__link"href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/tom-patton">LINKEDIN</a>
        <a class="contact__link" href="https://github.com/tompatton2">GITHUB</a>
        <!-- <a class="contact__link"href="">SKETCH</a> -->
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


